更加不是日本菜。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-1d68ecc4bd81046298b334370de3411e_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/633976111"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIuKCVwdbG2IoJEAMaCTEwMzE2MjExNyDPpsyrBjAAOIcDQC9yCTYzMzk3NjExMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1702210398.165188", "card_id": "Q_633497178", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 27}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么单片机上的程序不怎么使用 malloc，而 PC 上经常使用？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/633497178"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IuKCVwdbG2IoJEAMaCTEwMzA1NTc2MyDVtr6rBjAAOFtAMHIJNjMzNDk3MTc4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1702210398.165548", "card_id": "Q_632638211", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 140}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "父母的教育方式会对小孩有多大的影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我们中国人从小都是「棍棒底下出孝子」，但是我觉得不太适合现代社会的教育方式，我有个亲戚家的小孩，他妈妈是位老师，可能从小就对他的学习要求比较严格，导致他青春期异常叛逆，然后学习成绩大幅度下降，现在大学考都不考直接去读了大专，因为从小他不听话，不好好读书写作业就会被打，学习也是压着学。 大家能说说你们受到的教育方式和对自己孩子的教育方式是怎么教育的吗？现在挺迷茫的，和对象谈恋爱，问到结婚生小孩，我都不敢生就怕教育不好孩子，导致孩子抑郁症，或者各种心理问题，说这些还有些早了哈哈哈哈…… 各位公主王子可以留下一些教育方式给我参考一下！感谢各位公主王子~ 祝你们逢考必过！暴富！暴瘦！暴美！暴帅！嘿嘿嘿嘿！！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-def87362437f962d70c0a3f6163f9d63_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/632638211"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIu